34static void
35nv36_fb_tile_comp(struct nvkm_fb *fb, int i, u32 size, u32 flags,
36 struct nvkm_fb_tile *tile)
37{
38 u32 tiles = DIV_ROUND_UP(size, 0x40);
39 u32 tags = round_up(tiles / fb->ram->parts, 0x40);
40 if (!nvkm_mm_head(&fb->ram->tags, 0, 1, tags, tags, 1, &tile->tag)) {
41 if (flags & 2) tile->zcomp |= 0x10000000; /* Z16 */
42 else tile->zcomp |= 0x20000000; /* Z24S8 */
43 tile->zcomp |= ((tile->tag->offset ) >> 6);
44 tile->zcomp |= ((tile->tag->offset + tags - 1) >> 6) << 14;
45#ifdef __BIG_ENDIAN
46 tile->zcomp |= 0x80000000;
47#endif
48 }
49}
